    <description>Markdown Monster is an easy to use and extensible **Markdown Editor and Viewer** as well as a **Weblog Publishing** tool. 

This portable install is free standing, doesn't require an install and can install in non-admin mode. There is only one limitations compared to the full install: 

* No automatic `.md` and `.markdown` extension mapping

You can manually associate with **Open with -> Choose another application -> Markdown Monster**.

Markdown Monster sports syntax colored editing of Markdown text, inline spell checking, live HTML preview, embedding of images and links, and built-in support for screen captures. A few gentle toolbar helpers facilitate embedding content into your Markdown. The editor's goal is to let you focus on your content creation and get out of your way of your creativity.

You can publish your Markdown directly to your Weblog that supports WordPress or MetaWebLog APIs. You can manage multiple blogs and even download existing posts as Markdown.

Markdown Monster can also be extended using an easy, but powerful .NET based add-in model. 

Markdown Monster can be downloaded and evaluated for free and this package is unlimited and fully functional, but a [license](http://store.west-wind.com/product/markdown_monster) is required for continued use. Although Markdown Monster is licensed software, the source code is available in the open on GitHub.
    </description>
